Boots of Haste
Wondrous item, very rare (requires attunement)
While you wear these boots, you can click your heels
together to cast the haste spell on yourself as a bonus
action. You don’t suffer from lethargy when the spell

ends when cast using these boots. Once this prop-
erty is used, it can’t be used again until next dawn.

Boots of the Vigilant
Wondrous item, uncommon

While you wear these boots, you can sense impend-
ing danger. After you roll initiative, you can choose

to roll a d8 and add it to your initiative roll. Once

this property is used, it can’t be used again until the
next dawn.
