Houses of Kraghammer. Cataclysm bolts are usually
kept in sets of ten, though anyone who holds even
one can feel it thrumming with magical power. When
you hit with an attack using a cataclysm bolt, the
attack deals normal damage. Then roll a d6 on the
following table to determine its additional effect.
